   Define a function that converts Fahrenheit to Celsius.
   Ask the user, "What is the temperature in Fahrenheit?"
   (using input), and ultimately print out (x, "degrees
   Fahrenheit is ", y, "degrees Celsius.")

   (F - 32) * (5/9) = C
   ~~~~